recap-manila-2019.name: Recap: UXPH Roadshow 2019, Manila
recap-manila-2019.description: UXPH (User Experience Philippines) went back to the home court in Metro Manila to hold the last leg of the first National Roadshow carried out across the Philippines. UXPH Roadshow Manila was held on October 26, 2019 at the Globe Tower, Bonifacio Global City.

recap-cebu-2019.name: Recap: UXPH Roadshow 2019, Cebu
recap-cebu-2019.description: On August 31, 2019, UXPH (User Experience Philippines) held its first ever National Roadshow across the Philippines, starting in Cebu City.

recap-davao-2019.name: Recap: UXPH Roadshow 2019, Davao
recap-davao-2019.description: On September 28, 2019, UXPH (User Experience Philippines) held the second leg of their first ever National Roadshow across the Philippines, and landed in Davao City.

attending-asias-largest-ux-event-as-a-sc.name: Attending Asia’s largest UX event as a scholar!
attending-asias-largest-ux-event-as-a-sc.description: This will be my first time attending a UX+ Conference. I'm excited to learn from everyone's journey and their topics!

5-whys-one-must-see-uxplus-2020.name: 5 Whys one must see UX+ 2020
5-whys-one-must-see-uxplus-2020.description: This is not your usual five whys.

role-of-uxr-in-ph-rising-startup-scene.name: The Role of UXR in the Philippines’ Rising Startup Scene
role-of-uxr-in-ph-rising-startup-scene.description: UXRConf Anywhere 2020 imparted a wealth of takeaways that illustrates the invaluable impact that UXR can bring to our local tech community.

ready-set-research.name: Ready, Set, Research! 3 Things You Need to Know as a Fresh UX Researcher
ready-set-research.description: Starting always seems like the hardest, most intimidating part, but it doesn't have to be.

learning-to-be-inquisitve.name: Learning to be inquisitive: reflections from a beginner’s perspective
learning-to-be-inquisitve.description: UXRConf Anywhere 2020 brings to light a lot of things we need to be talking about in UX Research.
